Swapcoin Node
Welcome To The Brand-New Interface For Swapcoin Node!
Swapcoins Mined With Node Can't Be Published,Becuase They Need To Get Verified.
To Verify,Send Us A Message that Says:
"
[Verify token contract]
[name:<your name>]
[start:<date mining started>]
[amount:<swapcoins you mined>]
"
and we will check it soon.
